6. Apply Design Patterns
Purpose

Improve maintainability and scalability.

Factory Pattern Example
File: src/services/factory.py
class EmailService:

    def send(self):

        print("Sending Email")

class SMSService:

    def send(self):

        print("Sending SMS")

class NotificationFactory:

    @staticmethod
    def create(service_type):

        if service_type == "email":
            return EmailService()

        if service_type == "sms":
            return SMSService()
Usage
service = NotificationFactory.create("email")

service.send()
Benefits

✅ Clean architecture
✅ Easy maintenance
✅ Flexible design

